name: Homage to Matisse's Dancers
description: Artist: Vida Vakilotojar | Homage to Matisse Dance II | Method: For this piece I used two iPad apps, one to create individual dancer poses, and another to compose and overlay their images, and color the final result. After 7 years, I find the visible artifacts of the process interesting in their own way | Creation date: August 17, 2014
